::Zardus::

Zardus turns his head, looking at Wheeljack. He had never seen the bot 
before, but from what it was saying, it was obvious that he was part of the 
Alliance.

"Bloodystrike and Reptilica have mechanical skills, yes," he says in answer 
to the bot's question, "What does this weapon do?"
